        <item>
            <title>【MWC2025】Anker Solix Cloak 太阳能充电斗篷，外形似足 Jedi、30W USB-C 输出</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/04/anker-solix/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=anker-solix</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/04/anker-solix/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 09:22:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Anker]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ANKER Cloak]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MWC2025]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295239</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>ANKER 在西班牙举行的流动通讯展 MWC 2025 展示了一款太阳能充电概念外套 ANKER Solix Cloak，外套配备太阳能板，可为手机充电，外观设计酷似《星球大战》的绝地武士服装。这款外套以钙钛矿材料制成太阳能电池，并设有 30W USB-C 输出线，方便连接装置充电。产品目前仍属概念阶段，未知何时正式推出市场。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295498" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/472888929_5715948658-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/472888929_5715948658-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/472888929_5715948658.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/472888929_5715948658-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295499" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ggvc86_xsaaavkl-694x462.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ggvc86_xsaaavkl-694x462.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ggvc86_xsaaavkl-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295243" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>ANKER Solix 这款名为「Cloak（斗篷）」的太阳能外套，表面缝有 24 块钙钛矿太阳能电池，质感似布料且具一定柔韧性。外套设有 30W USB-C 输出，可接驳行动电源或直接为电子产品充电，适合户外活动时使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295244" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295245" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>外套设计上加入蓝色 LED 光条点缀帽边，提升夜间能见度兼具未来感，犹如科幻电影中的服装。外套外形似雨衣，轻巧并配有拉链，太阳能板分布于前胸、后背及右臂，右臂部分特别采用三角形设计，方便活动。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295246" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295248" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ankersolixcloak_rede-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295251" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot20250302at-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot20250302at-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot20250302at.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：CNET</p><p>据 CNET 报道，ANKER Solix 早前于 CES 2025 已展示其他太阳能产品，如即将推出的 EverFrost 2 冷却器及夏季发售的太阳能伞，显示其积极拓展太阳能应用领域。ANKER Solix 近年专注开发创新能源解决方案，除外套外，其太阳能伞及便携电源 SOLIX C200 亦备受瞩目，反映太阳能技术正逐步融入日常生活。业界人士预计，钙钛矿太阳能电池因成本低、效能高，未来或广泛应用于穿戴装置及户外用品。ANKER Solix 的太阳能外套于 Mobile World Congress 2025 亮相，以创新设计及实用功能吸引目光。虽然尚处概念阶段，但预料相关产品有望加速开发。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_56033"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-lId9_re3uc?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.cnet.com/tech/mobile/this-jacket-charges-your-phone-with-solar-energy-and-makes-you-look-like-a-jedi/">CNET</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
