        <item>
            <title>【MWC2025】Lenovo AI Stick 外置 AI 加速配件，配备 32 TOPS NPU，一插即加速电脑 AI 运算能力</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/04/lenovo-ai-stick/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lenovo-ai-stick</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/04/lenovo-ai-stick/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 08:49:01 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Lenovo AI Stick]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MWC2025]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295457</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>时下电脑都要讲 AI 处理能力，而一些用户希望为现有电脑提高 AI 处理能力，就可留意这件新产品。Lenovo 于世界流动通讯大会 MWC 2025 展示了一款全新「Lenovo AI Stick」，这款 USB-C 连接装置内置 32 TOPS NPU，专为提供 AI 加速运算而设计。今次我们就有记者到巴塞罗那看到这款新装置的真身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295458" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_092652-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_092652-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_092652-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>虽然 Lenovo AI Stick 目前仍属于概念产品，但其设计理念清晰，就是为现有电脑提供 AI 运算能力，特别是针对未内建 NPU 的系统，透过简单插入 USB-C 连接埠，即可运行 AI 模型及图像处理应用程式。</p><p>Lenovo 并未透露 AI Stick 内置 NPU 的供应商，但其官方资料显示，这款设备主要用于本地运行大型语言模型（LLM）及 AI 图像处理应用。AI Stick 兼容 Lenovo 自家的 AI Now 软件套件，该软件须在 Windows 11 及 x86 架构处理器上运行。装置透过 USB-C Thunderbolt 介面连接电脑，并具备侧面电源插口，若使用外部电源供应，NPU 运行速度可进一步提升，这也引发了外界对其 USB-C 供电效能的疑问。</p><p>除了增强 AI 运算能力，Lenovo 亦指出 AI Stick 可减少 GPU 占用，降低系统温度，对于已内建 NPU 或独立显示卡的设备来说，仍具备一定价值。这款设备的出现，为现有电脑提供了一种升级 AI 运算的便捷方案，尤其适合处理器性能强劲但缺乏 NPU 的装置，例如 Intel 即将推出的 Arrow Lake 平台。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295459" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_092634-694x563.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="563" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_092634-694x563.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_092634.jpg 1110w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/04/lenovo-ai-stick/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【MWC2025】Samsung S25 Edge 实物现身，多角度观赏超薄手机</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/04/samsung-s25-edge/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=samsung-s25-edge</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/04/samsung-s25-edge/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 08:40:40 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MWC2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[s25 edge]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[samsung]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295398</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Samsung 今年都有参加世界流动通讯展 MWC 2025，在会场中向公众展示 Samsung Galaxy S25 Edge 实物而且没有放在玻璃相内，另外利用 Android 平台、混合扩增实镜 AR 与虚拟实境的 Samsung Android XR 都有在会场展示。等我们 unwire 记者到巴塞罗那会场现场同大家睇睇。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295404" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093649-672x580.jpg" alt="" width="672" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093649-672x580.jpg 672w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093649-scaled.jpg 1043w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 672px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295399" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_110147-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_110147-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_110147.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Samsung Project Moohan XR 是三星与 Google 合作开发的产品，预计将于明年正式推出。Project Moohan 是首款采用 Android XR 平台，的装置， Android 将透过这个平台在，扩增实境 (AR) 和虚拟实境 (VR) 领域，进一步发展，平台未来将适用于 XR 头戴装置及智能眼镜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295400" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_110151-694x449.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="449" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_110151-694x449.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_110151.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Project Moohan 为全罩式头戴装置，外形设计类似 Apple Vision Pro。其名称「Moohan」源自韩文，意指「无限」，象征该装置提供广阔视野及高品质显示效果，以带来更沉浸式体验。使用者可透过 Google Maps 进行空间导航，观看，扩展视角的体育赛事，甚至利用 Gemini AI 助理规划旅行行程。</p><p>而更受现场观众关注的是 Samsung Galaxy S25 Edge。Galaxy S25 Edge 拥有超纤薄机身，为 S 系列历来最薄旗舰机款。三星在机身设计上采用更紧凑的内部结构，并透过改良散热技术及材料，确保装置在维持纤薄外型的同时，仍能提供强劲效能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1295401" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093712-428x580.jpg" alt="" width="555" height="752" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093712-428x580.jpg 428w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093712-scaled.jpg 664w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 555px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1295402" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093723-360x580.jpg" alt="" width="555" height="894" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093723-360x580.jpg 360w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093723-scaled.jpg 559w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 555px" /></p><p>装置搭载全新「Edge Display」，边框更窄，萤幕边缘曲线过渡更流畅，提升显示区域的视觉延伸感。三星也进一步强化 Dynamic AMOLED 2X 面板，提升色彩准确度与对比度，并支援 LTPO 技术，带来更流畅的自适应更新率，确保高效能与省电表现兼顾。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295403" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093735-694x523.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="523" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093735-694x523.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250303_093735-scaled.jpg 1195w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
